// Specific parser for Deadly Premonition UPDATA/PRM/SUBEVENT.PRM.
//
// SUBEVENT.PRM is a descriptor-based byte table. The PC file has 48 one-byte
// fields and 57 records. The record does not directly name the DSB file: the
// extracted UPDATA/EVENT/SUBEVENT DSBs use internal script ids such as 26, 27,
// 76..94, 102..108 and 268, while this PRM mainly contains a 1..50 local
// subevent sequence plus story/progress gating bytes.

LittleEndian();

